A treaty of peace and alliance was concluded between the two empires , and the limits of the East and West were defined by the right of present possession . 
But the Greeks soon forgot this humiliating equality , or remembered it only to hate the Barbarians by whom it was extorted . 
During the short union of virtue and power , they respectfully saluted the august Charlemagne , with the acclamations of basileus , and emperor of the Romans . 
The same controversy was revived in the reign of the Othos and their ambassador describes , in lively colors , the insolence of the Byzantine court . 
The Greeks affected to despise the poverty and ignorance of the Franks and Saxons and in their last decline refused to prostitute to the kings of Germany the title of Roman emperors . 
