In the minority of his son Otho the Third , Rome made a bold attempt to shake off the Saxon yoke , and the consul Crescentius was the Brutus of the republic . 
In the fortress of St . 
It was the design of Otho the Third to abandon the ruder countries of the North , to erect his throne in Italy , and to revive the institutions of the Roman monarchy . 
But his successors only once in their lives appeared on the banks of the Tyber , to receive their crown in the Vatican . 
Their absence was contemptible , their presence odious and formidable . 
They descended from the Alps , at the head of their barbarians , who were strangers and enemies to the country and their transient visit was a scene of tumult and bloodshed . 
