The earliest date of the Chaldaean observations is the year before Christ . 
After the conquest of Babylon by Alexander , they were communicated at the request of Aristotle , to the astronomer Hipparchus . 
rather excite than gratify our curiosity and the last of these writers confounds Sabianism with the primitive religion of the Arabs . 
But it is a slippery task to ascertain the creed of an ignorant people afraid and ashamed to disclose their secret traditions . 
