But they ascended the throne in a venerable or mature age and esteemed the domestic cares of religion and justice the most important duties of a sovereign . 
The austere and frugal measure of their lives was the effect of virtue or habit , and the pride of their simplicity insulted the vain magnificence of the kings of the earth . 
Oeeconomy is the source of liberality , and the increase of the revenue enabled Omar to establish a just and perpetual reward for the past and present services of the faithful . 
