Arabia was the temple and patrimony of the God of Mahomet but he beheld with less jealousy and affection the nations of the earth . 
In the eyes of an inquisitive polytheist , it must appear worthy of the human and the divine nature . 
The Harbii , as they are styled , qui tolerari nequeunt , are , . 
Those who , besides God , worship the sun , moon , or idols . 
In the extensive provinces of Persia and Africa , the national religion has been eradicated by the Mahometan faith . 
Their evil principle , the daemon Ahriman , might be represented as the rival , or as the creature , of the God of light . 
The temples of Persia were devoid of images but the worship of the sun and of fire might be stigmatized as a gross and criminal idolatry . 
A fanatic Iman deplored , in his sermons , the scandalous neighborhood , and accused the weakness or indifference of the faithful . 
with this holy and meritorious perjury . 
But the greatest part of the temples of Persia were ruined by the insensible and general desertion of their votaries . 
It was insensible , since it is not accompanied with any memorial of time or place , of persecution or resistance . 
