The Greeks were accompanied by the envoys of the great duke , or chagan , or czar , of the Russians . 
This Scandinavian origin of the people , or at least the princes , of Russia , may be confirmed and illustrated by the national annals and the general history of the North . 
The Normans , who had so long been concealed by a veil of impenetrable darkness , suddenly burst forth in the spirit of naval and military enterprise . 
Piracy was the exercise , the trade , the glory , and the virtue , of the Scandinavian youth . 
Their superiority in arms , discipline , and renown , commanded the fear and reverence of the natives . 
Their tyranny was expelled , their valor was again recalled , till at length Ruric , a Scandinavian chief , became the father of a dynasty which reigned above seven hundred years . 
