The three great nations of the world , the Greeks , the Saracens , and the Franks , encountered each other on the theatre of Italy . 
An offensive alliance was concluded between Basil the Macedonian , the first of his race , and Lewis the great grandson of Charlemagne and each party supplied the deficiencies of his associate . 
This important conquest had been achieved by the concord of the East and West but their recent amity was soon imbittered by the mutual complaints of jealousy and pride . 
His reply is expressed with the eloquence of indignation and truth We confess the magnitude of your preparation , says the great grandson of Charlemagne . 
