But these Italian conquests , this universal reign , soon escaped from the hand of the Greek emperor . 
The free cities of Lombardy no longer remembered their foreign benefactor , and without preserving the friendship of Ancona , he soon incurred the enmity of Venice . 
By his own avarice , or the complaints of his subjects , the Greek emperor was provoked to arrest the persons , and confiscate the effects , of the Venetian merchants . 
The Greeks accuse and magnify the wanton and sacrilegious cruelties that were perpetrated in the sack of Thessalonica , the second city of the empire . 
The former deplore the fate of those invincible but unsuspecting warriors who were destroyed by the arts of a vanquished foe . 
