Within this narrow verge , the Mahometans were still lodged in some impregnable castles and the husbandman , the trader , and the pilgrim , were exposed to daily and domestic hostility . 
The laws and language , the manners and titles , of the French nation and Latin church , were introduced into these transmarine colonies . 
